org.apache.calcite.rel.core

类 RelFactories

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.calcite.rel.core.RelFactories

  • public class RelFactories
extends Object
    Contains factory interface and default implementation for creating various rel nodes.

      • expandingScanFactory

        @Deprecated
 @Nonnull
public static RelFactories.TableScanFactory expandingScanFactory(@Nonnull
                                                                                       RelOptTable.ViewExpander viewExpander,
                                                                                       @Nonnull
                                                                                       RelFactories.TableScanFactory tableScanFactory)
        已过时。 Use the custom context Contexts.of(viewExpander) for RelBuilder.
        Creates a RelFactories.TableScanFactory that uses a RelOptTable.ViewExpander to handle TranslatableTable instances, and falls back to a default factory for other tables.
        参数:
        viewExpander - View expander
        tableScanFactory - Factory for non-translatable tables
        返回:
        Table scan factory
